---
title: Foolproof Apricot Chicken Drumsticks with Roasted Cauliflower & Celery Slaw
description: Mumbai-spiced chicken drumsticks pair perfectly with the sweet and fruity flavour of apricots for a match made in food heaven. Add a crunchy celery slaw for freshness and lots of texture and you’re on to a winner!

